  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5284663">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5284663/" class="title-link">1936年</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5284663"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/skyfreely/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1889456-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/skyfreely/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">sky</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-29"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-29 13:23:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5284663_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  很多年后的1936年，毛泽东在与美国记者斯诺的交谈中说：“由于父亲只准读孔孟经书和会计之类的书籍，所以我在深夜把屋子的窗户遮起，好使父亲看不见灯光。”他偷读的书中就有《盛世危言》，此书读毕，“激起我想要恢复学业的愿望”。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
